Description:
IMPECCABLY PRESENTED TOP QUALITY RESIDENCE!
Forget everything you've seen up until now! This property exudes quality and was built to the owners' own discerning standard.
Comprising three spacious bedrooms with an ensuite to the master and a centrally located bathroom to cater for everyone else. An open welcoming kitchen with top quality appliances and space to sit around and discuss the day's issues.
The large living area overlooks both the kitchen and the sensational outdoor living areas.
A fully enclosed alfresco with removable panels for year round entertaining, built in benches/storage cupboards and then more decking for when the grandkids come to visit so you can keep them out of the house while still being a part of their lives.
More? What about a garage with direct access and remote door, electric gates and brick fencing at the front for total security plus electric shutters all round so you can lock up and go on holidays any time you want. This list just goes on
YOU NEED TO SEE THIS HOME!

Description:
Development Opportunity in Residential Growth Zone! COUNCIL APPROVED PLANS
Located in the heart of Dandenong, this classic home is filled with character and set on an impressive block of approximately 989m2. The potential for this premium site is endless; retain the existing home and use the side access to develop the rear of the block (STCA), take advantage of the ‘Residential Growth Zone’ overlay and redevelop the entire site (potential for four storey increased density development STCA) or get on the fast track with the Council approved plans for 12 apartments with basement parking. The choice is yours!
The existing home comprises of a full length open plan meals, kitchen and family zone with light timber look flooring, feature ceilings and a lovely vista onto the rear garden. The large central kitchen includes an electric cooktop and wall oven, dishwasher, appliance cupboard, corner pantry and loads of bench and cupboard storage space. At the rear of the home is an additional rumpus room, perfect for a kids retreat, theatre room or 4th bedroom.
The light filled master bedroom delights with its high ceiling, decorative mouldings, walk in robe and en-suite. The two additional bedrooms are both spacious with large robes and have access to the central family bathroom. Other features of the home include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, walk in linen cupboard and an alarm system.
Outdoor features include a double carport, storage space with roller door access, large yard, two water tanks and a solar heated swimming pool.
Walking distance to St John’s Regional College, Dandenong Primary School and Dandenong Plaza and Market as well as being only minutes to Dandenong train station, Dandenong hospital and Chisholm TAFE and within easy access to the Monash Freeway, South Gippsland Hwy and Eastlink - location and opportunity don’t get any better than this!

Description:
A RARE OPPORTUNITY
A real estate opportunity like this doesn't come around too often; on offer we have a single storey 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, and a single car garage unit built to perfection and immaculately maintained. The unit being the last one on the block gives you a sense of privacy and 2 additional car parks.
Freshly painted throughout, this delightful unit is filled with sunlight with the bonus of a spacious courtyard. Wonderfully spacious throughout be the envy of all your friends with 2 large bedrooms both with BIR, with brand new carpet throughout the entire home there is nothing left to do but move in.
When you step inside the front entry you will be amazed by the size of the kitchen. Featuring plenty of storage, a breakfast bar, double sink and stainless steel appliances to suit all your entertaining needs. Relax with your guests as they enjoy the spacious lounge with adjoining meals area, with split system a/c. Access to rear courtyard via laundry or lounge for all your entertaining purposes.
Dandenong Amenities:
Nearest Primary Schools: Dandenong, St Gerard's, Dandenong South, Dandenong North, St Mary's, Dandenong West.
Nearest Secondary Schools: Dandenong, Cleeland Secondary College, Cornish College, St Johns Regional College

Nearest Transport:

Nearest Recreation: Dandenong Park, George Andrew Reserve, Heritage Hill Museum & Historic Gardens, Dandenong Bike Trail
Other Amenities: Close to Eastlink, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Plaza (inc. Kmart, Target, Coles, Woolworths, Local Take Away, Bakery, Chemist, Bank and Fresh Fruit/Vegetables) KFC, McDonalds, Subway, 24hr Coles, The Castle Music Venue, Reading Cinema

Wrapped in Charm and Character, made for Entertaining
Relax after a hard days work or invite all the friends and entertain in style in this wonderful family home. Immersed in manicured gardens front and rear, enter through the tiled portico and inviting hallway into the heart of the home, a welcoming kitchen and family room that opens via full length bi fold doors onto an expansive deck and picturesque backyard.
Sale By Set Date – Tuesday 28th November at 5pm (unless sold prior)
Even the front lounge room has access through French doors to a private paved front courtyard! Cooking in the gleaming modern kitchen with 900mm oven/cooktop is a breeze with quality double dishwasher and plenty of bench and cupboard space. Spacious master bedroom with sparkling ensuite featuring a double shower is sure to please, complimented by 2 further bedrooms and central main bathroom. Comforts include ducted heating and A/C, with the added bonus of bill saving solar panels and the 2 toilets connected to a rainwater tank.
Extras include double garage and long driveway to cater for all your car parking requirements, security system, plus extra garden shed for all you storage needs. Conveniently located close to train station & bus, East link access, park, schools, local shops as well as Dandenong CBD. Guaranteed to impress, inspect today!

Description:
Stunning Home in Central Dandenong’s Premier Pocket
Sitting in one of central Dandenong’s most sought after pockets this property makes a perfect home to live in or purchase as an investment to take advantage of the substantial capital growth. Immaculately presented internally the spacious cladded weatherboard dwelling comprises 3 good sized bedrooms with additional study or potentially a 4th bedroom, 2 bathrooms with central bathroom being renovated and the second bathroom being almost brand new, formal lounge and dining areas, well connected kitchen with ample storage and bench space as well as room for small breakfast table, brand new laundry and additional rear sunroom which allows for extra storage space or working space. Additionally the beautifully kept home provides all the necessary features including gas ducted heating, refrigerated cooling, immaculately polished floorboards throughout, secure roller shutters, 10 solar panels on the roof and loads of car parking space with double garage and carport which can easily accommodate 2 cars. With a generous land size of 644 sqm and potential to keep the front dwelling and build a small unit in the backyard (STCA) this property is perfect for all families, investors or small builders/developers. Arrange to inspect before it is too late!
Contact: Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467 or Theo Maric on 0411 410 744
Auction: Saturday 18th November 2017 at 11:30am, On Site
Terms: 10% Deposit, Balance in 60-90 Days
TO VIEW THE CONSUMER AFFAIRS DUE DILIGENCE CHECKLIST PLEASE VISIT http://www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist

Description:
Renovated 2 bedroom unit in the heart of Dandenong
This two bedroom plus study unit is set at the rear of a quiet complex and just minutes away from Dandenong Plaza, train station, local schools and it offers easy access to all amenities. Featuring:
- 2 spacious bedrooms plus study and master with double BIR's
- Spacious kitchen and dining area

Relax with a walk in the park located a footstep away from your own backyard and overlooking a tranquil reserve. With refurbished roofing plumbing and a single lock-up garage to complete the picture this is a mixture of convenience and relaxed lifestyle that is not to be missed!
